      "rationale": "Eleven constructs assembled from production-representative 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screws, 5.5 mm cobalt-chrome rods, and polyaxial tulips. Lot traceability documented. Assembly performed by trained technicians following clinical technique guide. Sample size exceeds minimum requirement for Medium decision consequence. Achieved level 3 meets requirement."
