      "rationale": "Per-specimen CMM geometry and per-lot material properties used to parameterise each of the 11 model instances. Set-screw torque recorded during assembly and mapped to preload via calibration curve. Input equivalency confirmed by overlay of FEA geometry on CMM point cloud (max deviation 0.04 mm). Achieved level 3 exceeds requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
