      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and absolute percent difference < 10% across 11 model-experiment pairs. Statistical analysis accounts for experimental measurement uncertainty (load cell calibration ±0.5%, displacement transducer ±0.1 mm) and model input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n=500 samples). Achieved level 3 meets requirement."
